    </para>
    <para xml:id="S2.p7">
      <p framecolor="#8080BF" backgroundcolor="white" framed="rectangle"><text cssstyle="display:block;width:100%;" color="#FFFFFF" backgroundcolor="#8080BF">A Titled Frame</text>
This is a titled frame.</p>
